<p>The Mad Money Machine is proud to advertise <a href="http://ifa.com/">Index Funds Advisors at ifa.com </a> <a href="http://ifa.com"><img title="IFA" src="http://MadMoneyMachine.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/01/ifalogo_jpg-760.jpg" alt="IFA" title="IFA" width="250" height="57" /> </a></p>
<h3><img src="http://madmoneymachine.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/01/mmm-142.jpg" border="0" alt="MMM-142" width="244" height="244" align="right" /> Topics in this week&#8217;s show include:</h3>
<ul>
<li>Computer is sick again!</li>
<li>Windows 7 on Fusion</li>
<li>Reagan&#8217;s Inauguration</li>
<li>Stock pickers blast the Lazy Portfolios</li>
<li>GURU: Harry Browne.<a href="http://crawlingroad.com/blog/2008/12/18/the-permanent-portfolio-allocation/"> Hear his radio show</a> talking about the four economic cycles and investments to own. (Thanks CrawlingRoad.com)</li>
<li>Bernie Madoff: Who do you trust? IFA not like him.</li>
<li>TOOL: NYTimes Graphic: <a href="http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2009/01/06/business/20090106-comeback-graphic.html">Calculate Your Financial Comeback</a></li>
<li>Barrons <a href="http://online.barrons.com/article/SB123094029415750267.html">says get out</a> of treasuries</li>
<li>Mish <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/MishsGlobalEconomicTrendAnalysis/~3/506846468/is-stock-market-cheap.html">says S&amp;P earnings are going lower</a> , P/E ratio of 15 would mean S&amp;P of 600 or less.</li>
<li>LEARNING EARNING: <a href="http://www.ifa.com/aboutus/">IFA Investment Principles</a> #3:  <a href="http://www.ifa.com/section/WhyPricesChange.asp">Free markets match prices  to current levels of uncertainty, so that buyers can  earn a risk-appropriate  return</a> .</li>
<li>Calls regarding where did the extra $10 come from on a $100 loan at 10%?</li>
<li><strong>Subscribe in iTunes to &quot;<a href="http://itunes.apple.com/WebObjects/MZStore.woa/wa/viewPodcast?id=296274081">Index Funds Advisors</a> &quot; podcast!</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Music from music.podshow.com:</span><br />
Runaway Train - <a href="http://music.podshow.com/music/producers/producerLibrary/artistdetails.php?BandHash=2fbb9841c81697b83f64e08fdf5310d7">Under Feather<br />
</a></p>
